Cell C Increased Both Revenue, Subscriber Numbers Last Year, Company Says

-- B y   J a n i c e   K e w
-- 
2011-08-11T08:39:28Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-08-11/cell-c-increased-both-revenue-subscriber-numbers-last-year-company-says.html
Cell C Ltd., a South African mobile-
network operator, reported an increase in revenue and its
subscriber base in 2010, Chief Executive Officer Simon Duffy
told reporters in Johannesburg today.  To contact the reporter on this story:
